reviewText: I bought this just for me magoriums wonder imporium, but I'm really glad i got all 4!
The movies worked fine. The seller did a great job shopping.
I love all of these! Good clean fun entertainment. The kids will love them as well. Each movie has an interesting message behind it.
My girls love watching these movies!
Bought this for Mr Magorium but my kid's love City of Ember and Nim's Island as well.
This movie was entertaining and at times pretty funny.  I would recommend this movie as something to watch and enjoy - but definitely not thought provoking.
